"""
        Test that the equality/inequality operators return False/True when
        comparing two ApplicationSpecificInformation objects with different
        data.
        """
a = attributes.ApplicationSpecificInformation(application_namespace=
    'test_namespace_1')
b = attributes.ApplicationSpecificInformation(application_namespace=
    'test_namespace_2')
self.assertFalse(a == b)
self.assertFalse(b == a)
self.assertTrue(a != b)
self.assertTrue(b != a)
